('coil-connector-pack','smart-coil-connector-pack','Smart Coil Connector Pack (4-Pin, VW/Audi Style)','Coil Connectors','4 × connector pigtails for common smart coils (VW/Audi 4-pin). Optional add-on.','A pack of 4 pre-wired connector pigtails for the ubiquitous VW/Audi-style 4-pin smart ignition coils. These coils are the most commonly used aftermarket COP solution for Speeduino builds. Saves time vs sourcing connectors individually.',900,'accessory','["v0.3","v0.4"]','VW/Audi-style smart coils','optional','[]','Beginner','3–5','["4 × 4-pin coil connector pigtails (~15 cm leads)"]','[]',NULL,0,1,'{"Quantity":"4 connectors","Compatibility":"VW/Audi 4-pin smart coils","Lead length":"~15 cm"}',340);

